headline: HR Software Stocks Q1 Teardown: Paychex (NASDAQ:PAYX) Vs The Rest
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how hr software stocks fared in Q1, starting with Paychex (NASDAQ:PAYX).
